+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
                          PURIFICATION
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

	Level: 2
	Cost: 40
	Text: purify

	With meditation am psionicist can focus his thoughts on cleaning
	his body of all poisons. With this power you can enter a meditation
	and clean all the poisons from your system.

